msgid ""
"Undoes any unsaved modifications to preferences back to the previous "
"saved state."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/introduction.rst:36
msgid "Auto-Save Preferences"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/introduction.rst:36
msgid ""
"Toggle whether or not the preferences are saved when exiting the "
"*Preferences* window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/introduction.rst:40
msgid ""
"It can be valuable to make a backup of your preferences in the event that"
" you lose your configuration."
msgstr ""
"Pode ser de grande valia, salvar uma cópia de segurança de suas "
"preferências para o caso de você haver perdido as suas configurações."

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/introduction.rst:42
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"See the :doc:`directory layout "
"</getting_started/configuration/directories>` section to see where your "
"preferences are stored."
msgstr ""
"Veja a página :doc:`esquema de diretórios "
"</getting_started/installing/configuration/directories>`, especificamente"
" a seção onde as suas preferências são guardadas."

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/introduction.rst:49
msgid "Load Factory Settings"
msgstr "Carregar as configurações de fábrica"

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/introduction.rst:51
msgid ""
"If you want to completely undo all the modifications made to the "
"preferences and revert them to the factory settings. Open the menu at the"
" bottom left and select *Load Factory Settings*. Note that no permanent "
"changes are made until you save the preferences or close the preferences "
"window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/preferences/introduction.rst:57
msgid ""
"Using this only resets the preferences and will not affect settings "
"stored in the startup file. This includes app templates, area locations, "
"and any Blender properties not part of the preferences."
msgstr ""

